Personal Information Collected Automatically:
We receive and store certain types of usage related information whenever you interact with Application. For example, RISE INDONESIA may automatically receive and record information regarding your computer’s IP address, browser information, Facebook user ID, Facebook Page fan status, and URLs accessed. Such information may be shared in aggregate (non-personally identifiable) form with our partners. 

